reviews.customers_say: Customers love this sweater's soft, feminine style with a cute pattern, and appreciate that it's true to size with plenty of room.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Sweater
items.body: So soft and very cute. I received a lot of compliments on it. Comfortable and not too hot. Colors are beautiful. Fits as expected. Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and warm
items.body: Soft, comfortable, fits well and looks great. I ordered another one in black. Read more
items.author: Sheila

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sleeves are along and wide but really nice sweater otherwise.
items.body: Sooo soft and cute! I hated to send it back but I did because the sleeves were very long and also wide. Had I studied the photo better, I might have seen that the sleeves were oversized. This fit every where else and was flattering in the black with white. I ordered the L and it fit like my usual size 12. This is a lighter weight sweater which I found perfect, and you cannot see through the knit. Wish they would fix those sleeves! Read more
items.author: Sandra F.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Warm,true fit.
items.body: This sweater feels very comfortable. It is not heavy and thick. It’s on the thinner side so perfect with jeans! The fit was perfect true a m. It feels cozy and not cheap plus had the perfect trio of orange white and grey. I highly recommend it and know many moms from my town have complimented me on and asked where I got it from. Read more
items.author: Crystal Anne Ramos

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great sweater!
items.body: I have now bought ten of these sweaters in different colors. I love them, the colors are true to the pictures and they’re soft and warm. I ordered large, my usual size and they have a loose comfortable fit. I can’t recommend them highly enough. I have other sweaters from Zeagoo and they are all really nice. I really love their tops. short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Nutmeg, Black B1, Army Green, Deep Gray, Black, Coffee, Dusty Blue, Orange, Colorblock 278, Rose Red, Colorblock Jh550, Lake Blue, Light Pink. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
